```mermaid
graph TD
    Start[Determine type of area to be classified by inspection of installation layout and process details] --> OpenArea[Open Area<br/>Open air conditions<br/>Wind speed rarely<br/>&lt;0.5m/sec. and<br/>frequently &gt;2.0m/sec<br/>D.2]
    Start --> EnclosedArea[Enclosed Area<br/>D.3]

    OpenArea --> Obstruction{Are there any<br/>Significant<br/>obstruction to<br/>natural wind<br/>ventilation<br/>D.2.2}

    Obstruction -- NO --> Result1[Open Area:<br/>Natural Ventilation<br/>D.2]
    Obstruction -- YES --> AirChanges{Is there &gt; 12 air changes/ hr by natural<br/>air movement over the whole area?<br/>D.3.1}

    EnclosedArea --> AirChanges

    AirChanges -- YES --> Result2[Sheltered Area:<br/>Restricted Natural<br/>Ventilation<br/>D.4]
    AirChanges -- NO --> InternalSource{Does enclosed area<br/>contain internal<br/>source of release?<br/>D.2.4}

    InternalSource -- YES --> ArtificialVent[Consider general or<br/>local artificial<br/>ventilation<br/>D.3.3]
    InternalSource -- NO --> ExternalSource{If external source<br/>exists, is enclosure<br/>pressurised against<br/>outside pressure<br/>of 50N/sqm?<br/>D.3.3.3}

    ExternalSource -- YES --> Result3[Enclosed Area:<br/>Non Hazardous<br/>D.3.3.3 and D.6.3<br/>Table D.2]
    ExternalSource -- NO --> VentSystem{Does ventilation<br/>system give<br/>&gt; 12 air changes/ hr?}

    VentSystem -- NO --> Result4[Enclosed Area:<br/>Inadequate Ventilation<br/>D.3.2<br/>Table D.1<br/>Consider redesign<br/>of ventilation system]
    VentSystem -- YES --> DilutionVent{Are there sufficient<br/>air changes to give<br/>dilution ventilation<br/>at all ignition<br/>sources?<br/>D.3.3.2}

    DilutionVent -- NO --> Result5[Enclosed Area:<br/>Adequate Ventilation<br/>D.6.1<br/>Tables D.1 and D.2]
    DilutionVent -- YES --> Result6[Enclosed Area:<br/>Dilution Ventilation<br/>D.6.2<br/>Tables D.1 and D.2<br/>Must be confirmed<br/>by Gas Dispersion<br/>Specialist]

    ArtificialVent --> ExternalSource
```

